author: Jessica Bennett
title: Cast of “Love & Hip Hop,” Then & Now
text:
NEXT Advertisement 
Love & Hip Hop: New York just completed its eighth season, making day one fans feel like we’ve known the cast forever! 
Of course that isn’t truly the case, as many L&HH cast members led completely different lives (and looked like completely different people) before the reality cameras started rolling. 
Check out the cast of Love & Hip Hop then and now in the photos above.
